{"tid":128341,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)刺客信條 監獄格鬥1-2","createTime":"2017-02-20T17:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T21:38:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5adc6164887979f7646ad67c95814b5844d6d673","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=add4466c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3beb0bf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6c/Assassin%27s_Creed_2016_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6c%2FAssassin%2527s_Creed_2016_Poster.jpg&h=677d9088&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/88/1b/e6/881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F88%2F1b%2Fe6%2F881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg&h=b296f060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://outalpha.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foutalpha.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FCZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg&h=47f076bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述職業罪犯柯倫&middot;林區透過阿布斯泰戈（Abstergo）科技公司察覺自己其實是刺客組織的後裔，他被迫參與測驗來進行深層記憶的探索，以便重溫祖先阿吉拉爾闖盪西班牙宗教裁判所的經歷。林區在探索的過程中，必須獲得其知識和技能，以面對聖殿及存於現今的敵人..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在前集過後的數年，前世界重量級拳王喬治&middot;「冰人」&middot;錢伯為了在退休時間賺點錢，便而前往俄羅斯拍廣告。在造訪當地進行的一系列的拳擊比賽時，他遭他人誣陷持有古柯鹼，而再度被送往監獄，但那裡的氣候卻比以前待的監獄還要寒冷。<br />\n在那他發現了該監獄官員安排的非法綜合格鬥賽，以助在外的大亨賺取賭金。為此，冰人與背後的大亨達成協議，只要打倒獄中最強的戰士尤里&middot;波卡就能重獲自由。但身手高超的幫派頭目尤里&middot;波卡為了成為世界最強的拳手，而與冰人不合，使得雙方的暴力戰役即將展開..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述繼前集的數年過後，右膝受傷的失去戰力的尤里&middot;波卡因自卑而引退，而改至廁所打掃。但因黑幫老大兼監獄格鬥的大亨嘎卡的緣故，使得尤里再次復出參戰。後來，尤里被轉送往喬治亞；在那，他除了面對喜歡碎碎念並與自己不合的美國人托波外，還要和來自他國的囚犯們展開廝殺<br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628eb906d57055c213c3f9c47c1c2a2f7c6b4b61","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e487cef52c47accab50714b3cf72f280f36c94f9","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bf2e2d06254f2fec96f153eeec6f63191ffe3f","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038c7001906abf71449dc3400d6989598f7d9f90","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25cc64f4a3a21e8e15b7f8ee7311cb8d01a02b5","tid":128341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj